a deadly ebola virus outbreak among imported 
laboratory monkeys apparently isnt harming people as evidenced by 
four animal handlers who have become infected but not sick 
the virus related to the deadly ebola virus of africa has 
turned up in monkeys from three philippine importers since fall 
