988 to 992 a 04 percent change that would translate into a 
50 percent growth over a full year 
its a signal that inflation is not going to quickly fade 
sinai said 
the governments household survey said that total employment 
rose slightly in march to 1183 million and that the labor force 
those employed or actively looking for work edged up to about 
1248 million a growth of about 200000 
the losses in factory payrolls were more than offset by gains in 
