novell is most successful in their field and we are leaders 
in ours so if you can bring them together in the fold of things 
its better for the customers manzi said 
mcsharry agreed with manzi 
in the shortterm it wont change the service provided to the 
customers but in the longterm it significantly changes the 
offerings mcsharry said youll see more industrywide 
software therell be more emphasis on group networked software 
